x = (data['Dist'])# mpc
y = data['Vel'] # km/s

def func(x, a, b):
    return a*x + b

popt1, pcov1 = curve_fit(func, x, y)

plt.plot(x, y, 'go')
plt.plot(x, np.polyval(popt1, x), 'r')
plt.text(20, 11000, r"a = {0:.3f} +/- {1:.3f}".format(popt1[0], pcov1[0,0]**0.5))
plt.xlabel("Distance (mpc)")
plt.ylabel("Velocity (km/s)")
plt.show()
